                                                <h5 class="card-title">Ocean Side Villa</h5>       
                                                <p class="card-text">Closest to the beach, the 150sqm Ocean Front Pool Villas are the epitome of luxury and elegance. A spacious living room leads on to the private pool. Down pillows, Irish linen and the world’s best bed ensure a good night’s sleep.</p>
                                                <tbody>
                                                    <tr>
